-- Saudi Industry Fund Gets Clearance to Raise Capital, Watan Says
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-04-04T06:39:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-04/saudi-industry-fund-gets-clearance-to-raise-capital-watan-says.html
The Saudi Industrial Development
Fund received royal approval to raise its capital to 40 billion
riyals ($11 billion) from 20 billion riyals,  al-Watan newspaper 
reported, citing Chairman  Abdulrahman Al-Hamidy .  To contact the reporter on this story:
